{%- comment -%}
  TechAura Footer Legal Compliance — Colombia
  ============================================
  Required legal information for Colombian e-commerce:
  - Company identification (NIT or Razón Social)
  - Ley 1581 de 2012 (Data Protection)
  - Ley 1480 de 2011 (Consumer Rights / Derecho de Retracto)
  - Contact information
  - Payment methods trust badges
  
  Usage: {% render 'footer-legal-colombia' %}
  Place after the main footer content, before closing </footer>
{%- endcomment -%}

<div class="footer-legal-colombia">
  <div class="page-width footer-legal-colombia__inner">
    
    {%- comment -%} Trust Badges Row {%- endcomment -%}
    <div class="footer-legal-colombia__trust">
      <div class="footer-legal-colombia__badge">
        {% render 'icon-system', icon: 'guarantee', size: 20, color: 'var(--ta-accent, #00D4AA)' %}
        <span>Garantía 30 Días</span>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-legal-colombia__badge">
        {% render 'icon-system', icon: 'shipping', size: 20, color: 'var(--ta-accent, #00D4AA)' %}
        <span>Envío Gratis 🇨🇴</span>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-legal-colombia__badge">
        {% render 'icon-system', icon: 'lock', size: 20, color: 'var(--ta-accent, #00D4AA)' %}
        <span>Pago Seguro SSL</span>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-legal-colombia__badge">
        {% render 'icon-system', icon: 'payment', size: 20, color: 'var(--ta-accent, #00D4AA)' %}
        <span>Pago Contraentrega</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    {%- comment -%} Payment Methods {%- endcomment -%}
    <div class="footer-legal-colombia__payments">
      <p class="footer-legal-colombia__payments-label">Métodos de pago aceptados:</p>
      <div class="footer-legal-colombia__payments-list">
        <span class="footer-legal-colombia__payment-method">💳 Tarjetas Crédito/Débito</span>
        <span class="footer-legal-colombia__payment-method">🏦 PSE</span>
        <span class="footer-legal-colombia__payment-method">📱 Nequi</span>
        <span class="footer-legal-colombia__payment-method">🏪 Efectivo Contraentrega</span>
        <span class="footer-legal-colombia__payment-method">🔄 Transferencia Bancaria</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    {%- comment -%} Legal Compliance {%- endcomment -%}
    <div class="footer-legal-colombia__legal">
      <p class="footer-legal-colombia__legal-text">
        TechAura — Tienda de Tecnología en Colombia
        <br>
        <small>
          Este sitio cumple con la <strong>Ley 1480 de 2011</strong> (Estatuto del Consumidor) y la <strong>Ley 1581 de 2012</strong> (Protección de Datos Personales).
          Derecho de retracto: 5 días hábiles desde la entrega del producto (Art. 47, Ley 1480/2011).
        </small>
      </p>
      <p class="footer-legal-colombia__legal-text">
        <small>
          Al realizar una compra en TechAura, aceptas nuestra 
          <a href="{{ pages['politica-de-privacidad'].url | default: '/policies/privacy-policy' }}">Política de Privacidad</a> y 
          <a href="{{ pages['terminos-y-condiciones'].url | default: '/policies/terms-of-service' }}">Términos y Condiciones</a>.
          Para solicitudes de datos personales (ARCO): contacto@techauraz.com
        </small>
      </p>
      <p class="footer-legal-colombia__legal-text">
        <small>WhatsApp: <a href="https://wa.me/573008602789">+57 300 860 2789</a> · Atención Lun-Sáb 8am-6pm COT</small>
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .footer-legal-colombia {
    background: var(--ta-bg-tertiary, #f1f5f9);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--ta-border, #e2e8f0);
    padding: 2.4rem 0 1.6rem;
  }

  .footer-legal-colombia__inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.6rem;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .footer-legal-colombia__trust {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1.6rem;
  }

  .footer-legal-colombia__badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ta-text, #0f172a);
    background: var(--ta-bg, #fff);
    padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
    border-radius: var(--ta-radius-pill, 999px);
    box-shadow: var(--ta-shadow-xs, 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05));
    border: 1px solid var(--ta-border, #e2e8f0);
  }

  .footer-legal-colombia__payments {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.8rem;
  }

  .footer-legal-colombia__payments-label {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--ta-text-muted, #64748b);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .footer-legal-colombia__payments-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .footer-legal-colombia__payment-method {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--ta-text-secondary, #1e293b);
    background: var(--ta-bg, #fff);
    padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
    border-radius: var(--ta-radius-sm, 4px);
    border: 1px solid var(--ta-border-light, #f1f5f9);
  }

  .footer-legal-colombia__legal {
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .footer-legal-colombia__legal-text {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--ta-text-muted, #64748b);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0 0 0.6rem;
  }

  .footer-legal-colombia__legal-text a {
    color: var(--ta-text-link, #2563EB);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .footer-legal-colombia__legal-text a:hover {
    color: var(--ta-primary, #1E3A5F);
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .footer-legal-colombia__trust {
      gap: 0.8rem;
    }

    .footer-legal-colombia__badge {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
